{"data":{"finishReason":"stop","message":"**SQL executed**\n\n```sql\nSELECT c.country,\n       SUM(o.amount) AS total_paid_amount\nFROM   orders AS o\nJOIN   customers AS c\n       ON o.customer_id = c.id\nWHERE  o.status = 'paid'\nGROUP BY c.country\nORDER BY c.country;\n```\n\n**Result**\n\n| country | total_paid_amount |\n|---------|-------------------|\n| DE      | 100.0 |\n| UK      | 2000.0 |\n| US      | 3000.5 |\n\nThe query sums the `amount` of all orders with status **paid**, grouping the totals by each customer's country.","sequence":0,"stepIndex":4,"turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"message.completed","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T11:00:46.017Z"}}
